              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thulium samples consisted of 11.1 mm diameter",
                "disks of 0.1 mm thickness. They were positioned at a",
                "distance of 2.5 cm from the neutron source.The",
                "thulium disks were sandwiched between two monitor",
                "foils of 197Au of the same diameter as the thulium",
                "disks and 0.025 mm thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
